        "message": "=Hi {{ $('Standardize Input').item.json.candidate_name }},\n\nThank you for submitting your details for the {{ $('Standardize Input').item.json.role }} position.\n\nAfter reviewing your profile against the job requirements, I'm afraid this particular role isn't the right fit at this time.\n\nIf you come across other openings that better match your background, feel free to submit again — I'd be happy to generate a tailored prep guide for you.\n\nAll the best with your job search!\n\nBest regards,\nAbhikalp Srivastava\nInterview Prep Assistant",
